snippet.textDisplay: Thanks Vince for explaining in lay man's terms the testing for SARS-CoV-2. Hope you have a speedy recovery. Hopefully the 21st century science for surviving viral pandemics will enable you to recover. Of course prevention is better than cure and I wonder how you could have prevented being infected? Hope your false positive test stays negative.
